 Thanks again for all your help! I think Sybil has something else for you now. But if you want, I have another job I need help with. A big, exciting one this time!  
  Color|purple|[I'm in. What do you need?]}}  
  Color|orange|[Aimee]}} 
 Alright, so. I don't know if you've ever seen the King's crown, but it looks ridiculous! his birthday is coming up so I've been commissioned to make a new one. I need three gems to do it, from more dangerous mines outside the city this time, think you can handle it?  
  Color|PURPLE|[I'm in, where should I look?]}}  
  Color|orange|[Aimee]}} 
 Yay, thank you so much! I need a garnet, malachite, and an onyx from three other mines. They're on the east and south parts of the swamp, and they're not the best but I do have some maps that should help if you want. 
  Color|PURPLE|[Nah, I like the silly crown]}}  
  &6[Aimee]}} 
 Really? He can't even see out of it! 
  Color|purple|[No, I'm sick of the mines.]}}  
  &6[Aimee]}} 
 Aww, I was hoping I could count on you. I didn't want to ask anyone else because it's supposed to be a secret project.  Header section 
&o  Head back to Aimee once you grab the garnet from the   Link   Eastern Mineshaft Eastern_Mineshaft wikilink  , malachite from the   Link   Southeastern Mineshaft Southeastern_Mineshaft wikilink  , and onyx from the   Link   Southern Mineshaft Southern_Mineshaft wikilink  . Header section_1 Table  AlignDefault ColWidthDefault AlignDefault 
