  Color|orange|[Aimee]}} 
 Wow, that was fast! I'll have plenty of time to finish this crown! Here, I have a tiara for you that makes you more healthy like the last one! I'll get working on the crown right away!  
  color|Purple|[Be careful, I think that Onyx might be cursed]}}  
  &6[Aimee]}} 
 Cursed? Don't be silly, there's no such thing as curses. They're a legend, like dragons and Septum.  
